{"word":"ἐπαγωνίζομαι","slug":"ἐπαγωνίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπαγωνίζομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to contend with</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> rei, <i>to contend for</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}